metadata.name: Barge Haulers on the Milky Way
metadata.description:
"Barge Haulers on the Volga" is a famous work by Ilya Repin. We have interpreted this plot in our own way, as it should look in the era of 3.0 ♦️
The picture shows a tug in the distance, as a symbol of progress, which does not reach ordinary people.

Collaboration with Painting Artist
https://foundation.app/@salliabrand
